rows.label: qev041003_MSG0020
rows.name:
Usually Zazazan get more reasonable bodyguards.
Looks like unlucky draw this time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0021
rows.name:
But contract is contract. We just have to get lazy friend
his iron sword, warrior assault rifle, and titanium shield,
in order to make him do job already.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0022
rows.name:
Meh-meh! Quit touching merchandise, Harvey!
That inventory very important![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0023
rows.name: Ha ha, whoops! You got it, boss.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0024
rows.name: So, uh, what exactly are we shipping here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0025
rows.name:
That is nothing Harvey need to worry about.
Just do what Zazazan pay you to do and keep it safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0026
rows.name: ...Ah, responsible friend is back! And the weapons?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0027
rows.name:
If friend has them, please hand them over.
First was iron sword...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0041
rows.name: Next was warrior assault rifle...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0042
rows.name: Third was titanium shield...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0028
rows.name: Good. Is Harvey happy now?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0029
rows.name:
Looks just fine to me. Should be more than enough to
keep you and your stock safe, boss.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0030
rows.name: Hmph. Zazazan wonder...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0031
rows.name:
What does friend think? Does Harvey seem capable
of protecting Zazazan?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_JNK0030
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev041003_SEL0031
rows.name: Say that Harvey looks skilled enough.

rows.label: qev041003_JNK0040
rows.name: Disagree

rows.label: qev041003_SEL0041
rows.name: Warn Zazazan that Harvey does not seem trustworthy.

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0032
rows.name:
Hmm. If friend says so, Zazazan will believe it.
Still, Zazazan should have hired you instead.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0033
rows.name: *sigh* Zazazan suppose it takes all kinds of friends.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0034
rows.name:
Zazazan agree. With Harvey as bodyguard, we may
not make it through Sylvalum in one piece.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0035
rows.name: *sigh* Zazazan should have hired you instead, friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0036
rows.name: In any case, thank you. Please take this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0037
rows.name: Heh heh. You two all done over there?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0038
rows.name:
Yes. Now we can leave. And maybe Harvey will learn
thing or two from hardworking friend here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0039
rows.name:
Will do, boss! Now that I've got a weapon,
ain't nothing out there can stand in my way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041003_MSG0040
rows.name:
Time to hit the road for home sweet home.
Next stop, New LA![ST:wait ]
